      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776022650810,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Designing GoogleDocs\n- stateful services, realtime updates, collaborative editing\n\n",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Designing GoogleDocs\n- stateful services, realtime updates, collaborative editing\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "5fuKjw4OpKZBj0-kRKKYk",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 275.3668166224363,
      "y": 312.1161621775891,
      "width": 473.11962890625,
      "height": 350,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a3",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 41477285,
      "version": 341,
      "versionNonce": 73357709,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776442710636,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Functional requirements\n\n- create new documents\n- make edits to the doc\n- view doc/edits from multiple users concurrently\n- cursor position of users are visible\n\nbelow the line\n---------------\n- permissions for the doc\n- specialized formatting\n- versioning\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Functional requirements\n\n- create new documents\n- make edits to the doc\n- view doc/edits from multiple users concurrently\n- cursor position of users are visible\n\nbelow the line\n---------------\n- permissions for the doc\n- specialized formatting\n- versioning\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "y11DG1fHzkDftY45D0WOr",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 263.7001770825058,
      "y": 697.8939399553667,
      "width": 518.6397094726562,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a5",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1558253573,
      "version": 422,
      "versionNonce": 1337368557,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776442710636,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Non-functional requirements\n\n- durable docs (persistence storage)\n- updates to the doc should be low latency (<100ms)\n- scale to 100M users overall\n- no more than 100 editors per doc\n- eventual consistency of edits",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Non-functional requirements\n\n- durable docs (persistence storage)\n- updates to the doc should be low latency (<100ms)\n- scale to 100M users overall\n- no more than 100 editors per doc\n- eventual consistency of edits",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "AJTik9-ZFWVkGA-vC7UpB",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 275.3946308517658,
      "y": 935.3994865251912,
      "width": 283.5597839355469,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a6",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 110681899,
      "version": 146,
      "versionNonce": 286661197,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776442710636,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Core Entities\n\nEditor / Viewer\nDocuments\nEdits (key press / deletions)\nCursor\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Core Entities\n\nEditor / Viewer\nDocuments\nEdits (key press / deletions)\nCursor\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "MBJJJXaPvQJ9Dr_Etu5D7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 273.1446079635822,
      "y": 1121.6494865251912,
      "width": 214.5398712158203,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a7",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1834048197,
      "version": 88,
      "versionNonce": 1096239277,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776442710636,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "API\n\nPOST /docs -> docId\n{\n    title : string\n}",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "API\n\nPOST /docs -> docId\n{\n    title : string\n}",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "p233cxoJ_LEGwfZkWUa2j",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 262.6446622170545,
      "y": 1325.038361850712,
      "width": 569.1995849609375,
      "height": 475,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aA",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 382055339,
      "version": 655,
      "versionNonce": 35891981,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776442710636,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "ws /docs/{docId}\n    SEND\n    {\n       type : \"insert\" | \"delete\"\n        ...\n    }\n    \n    // receive actual updates and the cursor for that user\n    RECV\n    {\n       type : \"update\" \n       ...\n    }\n\n    SEND\n    {\n       type : \"updateCursor\"\n        ...\n    }",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "ws /docs/{docId}\n    SEND\n    {\n       type : \"insert\" | \"delete\"\n        ...\n    }\n    \n    // receive actual updates and the cursor for that user\n    RECV\n    {\n       type : \"update\" \n       ...\n    }\n\n    SEND\n    {\n       type : \"updateCursor\"\n        ...\n    }",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "fo2FBwf92C1JaWL5UlTds",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -149.7222044203018,
      "y": 1339.3111623128257,
      "width": 357.4237060546875,
      "height": 60,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aC",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 229494667,
      "version": 361,
      "versionNonce": 880682699,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776022447668,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "When users send and http req to this url,\n the server will respond with a ws connection \nover the tcp conn already made for updates",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "When users send and http req to this url,\n the server will respond with a ws connection \nover the tcp conn already made for updates",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "rVASBAD2ElgjXnS4UB8so",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -120.98414623926561,
      "y": 1505.398382519919,
      "width": 286.76776123046875,
      "height": 80,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aE",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1220629957,
      "version": 231,
      "versionNonce": 847206885,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776022446423,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "When updates happen, it \nwill be pushed to all the\nusers except the one who created it\nover the ws conn ",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "When updates happen, it \nwill be pushed to all the\nusers except the one who created it\nover the ws conn ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
