    },
    {
      "id": "zjVhcP4KTFgSmMfjxZ2Vi",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 938.941082720951,
      "y": 1784.3233989729058,
      "width": 414.09823090904763,
      "height": 450,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b05",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1030424835,
      "version": 892,
      "versionNonce": 1055229389,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776440634604,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Since we are using OT and Cursor memory-\nmap, we need to keep all users of the\nsame docId connected to a single\nDocument service.\n\nZookeeper is the service registry, it\nkeeps track of all the Document services\nand their count.\nWhen a user connects to any Document\nservice, the Document service keeps a\nhash function to hash the docId, get the\ncorrect service that the user needs to\nconnect to from Zookeeper and sends a\nHTTP redirect to the user.\n\nThis design doesn't need the API\nGateway to connect to the Zookeeper\nand worry about Consistent hashing",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Since we are using OT and Cursor memory-map, we need to keep all users of the\nsame docId connected to a single Document service.\n\nZookeeper is the service registry, it keeps track of all the Document services and their count.\nWhen a user connects to any Document service, the Document service keeps a hash function to hash the docId, get the correct service that the user needs to connect to from Zookeeper and sends a HTTP redirect to the user.\n\nThis design doesn't need the API Gateway to connect to the Zookeeper and worry about Consistent hashing",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "aE2Fv_hs3LEYhMM7KFmAM",
